Sentence: ( A) Immunoblot and densitometric analysis of p53 / p21 signaling [ total p53, p53 - P ( ser18) and p21] in cerebellum of Ptc1 +/-, Rad54 -/-/ Ptc1 +/-, Parp - 1 -/-/ Ptc1 +/-, and Rad54 -/-/ Parp - 1 -/-/ Ptc1 +/- mice at P1, and ( B) in MEFs from Ptc1 +/- and Rad54 -/-/ Parp - 1 -/-/ Ptc1 +/- mice ( two independent cell lines per genotype ); β - actin and HSP70 were used as loading controls. ( C) Growth kinetics and ( D) quantification of SA - β - GAL staining in MEFs from Ptc1 +/- and Rad54 -/-/ Parp - 1 -/-/ Ptc1 +/- mouse embryos. ( E) Representative images of SA - β - GAL staining in MEFs from Ptc1 +/-, and ( F) and Rad54 -/-/ Parp - 1 -/-/ Ptc1 +/- mouse embryos. ( G - L) Proliferation ( Ki67) and ( M - R) DNA damage ( γ - H2AX) in different tissues from Ptc1 +/- and Rad54 -/-/ Parp - 1 -/-/ Ptc1 +/- neonatal mice at P1.
